自11月26日起，多明尼加民眾慶祝[水泥廠](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/24/dominican-
republic-against-the-cement-factory-in-los-haitises/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/24/dominican-republic-against-the-
cement-factory-in-los-haitises/")將搬遷，不會在原本預定的[Los
Haitises國家公園](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Los_Haitises_National_Park
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Los_Haitises_National_Park")興建，雖然建廠計畫獲得極大支持，但面對[多明尼加聯合國發展計畫否決](http://www.hoy.com.do/el-
pais/2009/11/26/303612/PNUD-rechaza-instalacion-de-cementera-en-Los-Haitises
"http://www.hoy.com.do/el-pais/2009/11/26/303612/PNUD-rechaza-instalacion-de-
cementera-en-Los-Haitises")，再加上社會大眾抗議，讓[多明尼加礦業集團](http://www.comidom.com/
"http://www.comidom.com/")決定順應民意。

包括部落格、Facebook與[Twitter](http://twitter.com/search?q=cementera%20los%20haitises
"http://twitter.com/search?q=cementera%20los%20haitises")上都有許多反應，例如[Amelia
Odette](http://twitter.com/AmeliaOdette/status/6091887444
"http://twitter.com/AmeliaOdette/status/6091887444")就為這項決定而歡呼：

> 很開心！水泥廠不建了！聯合國的報告強調，水泥廠不會出現在Los Haitises國家公園附近！只要團結就能達成目標！恭喜大家！

[![Los Haitises, photo used with permission of the Secretary of Environment,
Dominican Republic](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2009/12/haitises-300x128.jpg)](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2009/12/haitises.jpg)

